file.name: oapi.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http: //localhost:3333'
paths:
  '/user':
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              '$ref': '#/components/schemas/User'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Newly Created User
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                '$ref': '#/components/schemas/NewUser'
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Loaded User
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                '$ref': '#/components/schemas/User'
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      properties:
        email:
          type: string
      required:
        - email
    NewUser:
      properties:
        result:
          type: string
        user:
          '$ref': '#/components/schemas/User'
      required:
        - result
        - user
